  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into large bite-sized pieces</p>\n<p>Add them to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook over a high heat for 10-15 min or until fork-tender, then drain </p>",
