          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1726.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p>\n<p>Carefully wipe the pan clean </p>\n<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> fish cakes </strong>and cook on each side for 2-3 min until golden and crispy</p>\n<p>Tip: try not to fiddle with the fishcakes in the pan while they <span class=\"text-highlight\">cook so they</span> hold their shape</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1726.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1726.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
