          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1726.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fish cakes</strong> with the<strong> green beans</strong> to the side</p>\n<p>Drizzle over the<strong> lemon mayo </strong></p>\n<p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining lemon wedge</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
